profile:
Halton Handyman provides a one-stop-shop solution for clients in need of house repairs, renos, improvements, and installation services. I have built up client trust through providing exceptional customer service experiences and maintaining that trust with every visit. The services include consultation as well as the execution of projects promptly. Halton Handyman understands the importance of paying attention to detail to make it done right and remain within the client's budget. 

Services Provided:
Repairs, Upgrades, and Installation
Painting and Decorating
Flooring and Tiling
Renovations and mush more. 

EXPERIENCE & KNOWLEDGE
I combine quality workmanship, superior knowledge and low prices to provide you with service unmatched by other competitors.

BEST MATERIALS
My project management experience combined with my construction knowledge and skills will make the project run smoothly. I will ensure that the job is done right in timely manner.

PROFESSIONAL STANDARDS
My project management process involve a carefully planned series of steps, centred around a schedule I stick to and communicate daily with client about the on going progress.

If these are important to you as well then kindly give me a call and we'll see what Halton Handyman could do for you and your family.
Halton Handyman Team

profile:
At Silicone Seals, our goal is to make sure you get quality service for what you need.
 We specialize in a variety of services to take care of the big and small things your home needs.
 Whether you need sealant in your bathroom, or caulking around windows and doors, we got you covered.

We believe that our exceptional customer service, and quality work makes many happy customers. Contact us today to get a FREE QUOTE for your home.
services:
Our Primary Services:

- replacing caulking that is moldy and falling apart in your bathroom or kitchen

- caulking and sealing around masonry, concrete, decking/porch, and foundations

- draft sealing (foaming), using the highest quality low, medium, and high expansion foam and insulations, from todays leading manufactures. Let us get rid of those cold air drafts inside your home, and get you winter ready

- repairing or replacing caulking around windows and doors, using the highest grade of, silicone, polyurethane, acrylic or elastomeric sealants 

- caulking new windows and doors (new construction or installation) 

- Indoor and outdoor 

We also specialize in:
- repairing Interior water/moisture damage due to failed caulking or leaks, including drywall, ceiling, and floor repair.

- window and door trim repair.

- weather striping and threshold installation 

- stud and joist repair/replacing. Painting/repainting damaged or new surfaces. 

- epoxy and acrylic sealers over concrete, masonry, hardscaping and many other surfaces 

- restoring, staining and sealing wooden decks, fences, gazebos and docks 

- power washing and refreshing old masonry and concrete 

- we also offer grading and hardscaping as part of improving your homes water diversion, and prevent icing. Including, limestone screening, weed barrier, gravel, HPB, decorative river/quarry rock, interlocking, retaining wall, (both masonry, and lumber) and flag stone repairs and installation.

profile:
Hi there, I'm The Handyman Dan. I specialize in the smaller repair, maintenance, and home improvement projects. Do you have a broken screen door or a light fixture that needs installing? Then Dan is your man. Maybe you have a larger job to do like installing new tile in your front hallway, a new counter top or backsplash in the kitchen, or a new bathroom vanity. Perhaps you have a storage problem that a custom shelving unit would solve. Whatever small project you have I have the experience and the know-how to get it done right and get it done fast. The Handyman Dan's affordable hourly rate covers not just labour, but the right tools for the job, and travel expenses. Check out a sample To Do List at www.thehandymandan.com for a list of things I can help you with. If you don't see it on the list, give me a call. For most of the small jobs I can give you an estimate over the phone based on how long a similar job to yours would take. My workmanship is guaranteed so you can expect your job done right.
Give me a call today!
